                    <h4>The "Net Life Hour" Formula</h4>
                    <pre><code>Net Life Hour = 

(Gross Revenue - Hard Costs - "Sanity Tax") 
-------------------------------------------
     (Delivery Hours + Anxiety Hours)</code></pre>
                    <ul>
