                        <li><strong>Sanity Tax:</strong> The estimated cost of recovery (e.g., 2 hours of doom-scrolling after a toxic meeting).</li>
                        <li><strong>Anxiety Hours:</strong> Time spent thinking about the work while not doing it.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

